note.p: Landowner. Daughter of Francis De la Cour (1758–1825) and his wife Ann Boreham (1773–1852). Resided at ‘North Side of High Street’, Frindsbury, Rochester, Kent, 1881.
Census returns of England and Wales 1851 (The National Archives: Public Record Office HO107/1610/162/24), 1881 (RG11/881/71/21)
